284
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:05,400
I heard the report

285
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:07,280
and rushed here as soon as possible.

286
00:17:07,280 --> 00:17:08,200
We too,

287
00:17:08,319 --> 00:17:11,180
rushed here immediately after hearing the report.

288
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:17,079
You brought chicken legs from the yamen?

289
00:17:17,079 --> 00:17:18,680
I've checked it, no problem.

290
00:17:18,760 --> 00:17:20,680
Are you craving it, kid?

291
00:17:20,760 --> 00:17:22,760
How dare you talk about your old man?

292
00:17:23,560 --> 00:17:24,200
Coroner Li,

293
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:26,359
what are the details?

294
00:17:33,560 --> 00:17:35,920
The skeleton is relatively short.

295
00:17:36,080 --> 00:17:39,240
According to the measurement and estimation, it should be about four feet.

296
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:41,760
Judging from the growth cycle of children,

297
00:17:41,840 --> 00:17:42,720
the height of this skeleton

298
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:45,560
is consistent with that of a ten-year-old child.

299
00:17:46,640 --> 00:17:48,440
Looking at its slender bones

300
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:49,640
and light weight,

301
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:51,610
it should be around forty catties.

302
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,560
Checking its bone development characteristics,

303
00:17:53,560 --> 00:17:55,420
its pelvis is relatively narrow,

304
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:56,480
so it is judged to be

305
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:57,740
the skeleton of a girl.

306
00:18:03,080 --> 00:18:04,080
At the skull,

307
00:18:04,360 --> 00:18:06,690
there are obvious signs of being hit hard.

308
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:10,560
There is also a fracture at the frontal bone.

309
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:11,600
According to this speculation,

310
00:18:11,600 --> 00:18:13,200
the suspect should be holding a murder weapon,

311
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:14,480
