312
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:15,960
and slamming the back of her head.

313
00:18:15,960 --> 00:18:20,440
The victim fell to the ground and hit a sharp object with her forehead at the same time.

314
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:22,840
Look at the condition of the neck bones again.

315
00:18:22,840 --> 00:18:25,600
The suspect strangled the victim from behind,

316
00:18:25,760 --> 00:18:28,560
causing the neck bones to fold inward.

317
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:30,240
Su Lang.

318
00:18:31,360 --> 00:18:33,480
What's wrong, sister? What do you need?

319
00:18:33,480 --> 00:18:34,960
If strangling face to face,

320
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:36,820
