321
00:18:37,520 --> 00:18:38,250
In this case,

322
00:18:38,440 --> 00:18:39,840
would it face downward?

323
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:41,280
Got it.

324
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:42,360
Are you okay?

325
00:18:46,040 --> 00:18:48,170
What about the specific time of death?

326
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:51,880
Based on the weathering of the bones

327
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:53,960
