328
00:18:54,040 --> 00:18:55,400
the time of death

329
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:56,850
was eight years ago.

330
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:58,320
Eight years.

331
00:18:58,400 --> 00:19:01,060
The suspect chose to attack a ten-year-old girl

332
00:19:01,080 --> 00:19:02,280
from behind.

333
00:19:02,440 --> 00:19:03,440
You do it, Father.

334
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:06,880
He strangled her to death

335
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:09,000
before even turning her over.

336
00:19:09,240 --> 00:19:09,960
This means

337
00:19:10,120 --> 00:19:11,800
