341
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:16,960
We are acquaintances.

342
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:19,800
Miss Li.

343
00:19:20,520 --> 00:19:21,600
If you call me that again,

344
00:19:21,600 --> 00:19:23,330
I'll have my father punish you.

345
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:25,800
Coroner Li.

346
00:19:25,920 --> 00:19:27,440
To deduce so many details

347
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:29,240
from just a simple corpse,

348
00:19:29,280 --> 00:19:30,800
you are amazing.

349
00:19:31,320 --> 00:19:32,640
Did you all hear that clearly?

350
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:34,280
Coroner Li has already analyzed the case

351
00:19:34,280 --> 00:19:35,560
