352
00:19:35,560 --> 00:19:36,680
Go investigate right away.

353
00:19:36,680 --> 00:19:37,680
Within a radius of a hundred miles,

354
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:39,760
find out whose ten-year-old child died eight years ago.

355
00:19:39,760 --> 00:19:41,200
First, identify the deceased,

356
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:42,080
then through her identity,

357
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:43,240
