358
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:44,120
Everyone must be screened.

359
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:45,040
Understood?

360
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:46,600
Thief!

361
00:19:46,800 --> 00:19:47,640
Catch the thief!

362
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:48,600
Follow me.

363
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:54,360
Safety comes first, the case can wait.

364
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:01,400
All right, stop staring.

365
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:02,680
Hurry up and pack the bones,

366
00:20:02,680 --> 00:20:03,720
