367
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:04,560
Yes.

368
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:06,560
This petty thief...

369
00:20:07,320 --> 00:20:10,000
Every family is preparing to worship their ancestors for the New Year,

370
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:12,920
