371
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:15,160
You sure know how to pick a day.

372
00:20:24,360 --> 00:20:25,440
What are you staring at?

373
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:26,360
Chase him!

374
00:20:53,040 --> 00:20:54,240
Father, let's split up!

375
00:20:54,240 --> 00:20:55,320
Excuse me!

376
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:19,050
What are you staring at?

377
00:21:19,280 --> 00:21:20,000
Okay.

378
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:38,960
Excuse me.

379
00:22:07,680 --> 00:22:08,560
Excuse me!

380
00:22:08,600 --> 00:22:09,400
My cart!

381
00:22:12,080 --> 00:22:12,920
Su Lang,

382
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:14,320
I'm coming to save you.

383
00:22:37,520 --> 00:22:38,400
I'm sorry.

384
00:22:38,440 --> 00:22:39,560
I was careless

385
00:22:39,600 --> 00:22:41,000
and blocked your way to the afterlife.

386
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:42,720
I'll burn more paper money for you later

387
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:43,720
