388
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:44,760
I'm sorry.

389
00:22:51,560 --> 00:22:53,440
What's going on here?

390
00:23:00,280 --> 00:23:00,960
Everyone.

391
00:23:03,280 --> 00:23:04,560
Don't panic, everyone.

392
00:23:04,560 --> 00:23:06,820
My brother went missing half a month ago.

393
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:08,840
Apart from the remaining bloodstains at home,

394
00:23:08,840 --> 00:23:10,900
there are no other suspicious clues.

395
00:23:11,440 --> 00:23:12,440
I suspect

396
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:13,940
