400
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:23,480
He pretended to be a corpse and lay in a coffin,

401
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:26,440
hoping to find inspiration for solving the case while being transported.

402
00:23:26,440 --> 00:23:28,040
Since he's been missing for half a month,

403
00:23:28,040 --> 00:23:29,640
