404
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:30,480
I did.

405
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:32,800
But there are simply no results.

406
00:23:32,800 --> 00:23:33,920
Since there are no results,

407
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:35,120
you should wait at home.

408
00:23:35,120 --> 00:23:37,000
You will be notified naturally when there's news.

409
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:37,800
What's the use of

410
00:23:37,800 --> 00:23:39,660
you looking for a charlatan here?

411
00:23:41,320 --> 00:23:42,380
Don't panic, miss.

412
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:45,440
Please recount the details of the case.

413
00:23:47,760 --> 00:23:49,040
My brother, Wang Kang,

414
00:23:49,160 --> 00:23:51,720
has always run the coffin shop at the corner of the street.

415
00:23:51,720 --> 00:23:54,120
He makes a living by transporting corpses.

416
00:23:54,560 --> 00:23:55,640
My name is Wang Mingzhu,

417
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,800
his biological sister.

418
00:23:56,800 --> 00:23:59,120
I usually live at the Yichun Brothel,

419
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:01,130
and occasionally return home.

420
00:24:01,280 --> 00:24:02,920
My brother has been missing for days,

421
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:04,880
and the authorities have no news from their investigation.

422
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:06,920
I am filled with worry and doubt.

423
00:24:07,680 --> 00:24:09,720
The madam saw me looking devastated

424
00:24:09,800 --> 00:24:11,920
and frowning all day,

425
00:24:11,960 --> 00:24:14,690
so she dragged me to the backyard to find Jueming,

426
00:24:14,880 --> 00:24:17,040
hoping he could help me find a solution.

427
00:24:17,040 --> 00:24:18,900
This is my brother's coffin shop.

428
00:24:18,920 --> 00:24:20,600
What my brother used to do every day

429
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:23,520
was transport these coffins with corpses to the suburbs.

430
00:24:23,520 --> 00:24:25,320
Naturally, the relatives of the deceased

431
00:24:25,320 --> 00:24:27,450
would wait by the road to receive them.

432
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:29,160
Then they would carry the corpses together

433
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:30,920
into the mountains for burial.

434
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,240
On the day he went missing,

435
00:24:32,240 --> 00:24:34,280
someone still saw my brother.

436
00:24:35,320 --> 00:24:36,160
At night,

437
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:38,440
he transported coffins back and forth.

438
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:39,560
Why are you so sure

439
00:24:39,680 --> 00:24:41,140
that he has been murdered?

440
00:24:41,760 --> 00:24:42,480
This...

441
00:24:44,360 --> 00:24:45,840
This extra pool of blood,

442
00:24:46,120 --> 00:24:47,850
I don't know where it came from.

443
00:24:47,880 --> 00:24:50,120
Previously, my brother and I agreed

444
00:24:50,800 --> 00:24:53,920
to offer sacrifices to our parents before the Ghost Festival.

445
00:24:53,920 --> 00:24:56,040
But he has been missing.

446
00:24:56,720 --> 00:24:58,800
He had never left the shop before.

447
00:24:59,080 --> 00:25:00,010
This inevitably

448
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:01,570
makes me think too much.

449
00:25:03,800 --> 00:25:05,600
The last time Wang Kang transported a coffin,

450
00:25:05,600 --> 00:25:07,200
he was still seen by someone.

451
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:09,120
Can anyone testify?

452
00:25:11,600 --> 00:25:13,000
Although I can't see,

453
00:25:13,040 --> 00:25:15,280
my cane did indeed hit

454
00:25:15,320 --> 00:25:17,080
the horse's leg that night.

455
00:25:17,520 --> 00:25:19,920
The horse was startled, and the coffin fell to the ground.

456
00:25:19,920 --> 00:25:20,880
I felt it,

457
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:22,640
and it was a coffin that fell to the ground.

458
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:23,600
I knew

459
00:25:23,680 --> 00:25:25,360
I bumped into the coffin transport cart.

460
00:25:25,360 --> 00:25:27,360
I hurriedly apologized repeatedly

461
00:25:27,440 --> 00:25:30,560
and helped him carry the coffin onto the carriage.

462
00:25:30,720 --> 00:25:32,480
My brother's daily route for transporting coffins

463
00:25:32,480 --> 00:25:33,610
was always the same.

464
00:25:35,120 --> 00:25:36,520
Near where the collision happened,

465
00:25:36,520 --> 00:25:38,560
I picked up this piece of coffin wood.

466
00:25:38,560 --> 00:25:41,220
It proves that Blind Zhang is telling the truth.

467
00:25:51,760 --> 00:25:52,880
The route for transporting coffins,

468
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:53,760
do you know it?

469
00:25:55,080 --> 00:25:56,880
This horse knows the way better than I do.

470
00:25:56,880 --> 00:25:57,880
It can get there,

471
00:25:58,280 --> 00:25:59,400
then it's easy.

472
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:00,800
Put me in the coffin,

473
00:26:01,320 --> 00:26:02,650
and let it give me a ride.

474
00:26:02,800 --> 00:26:04,860
What does Wang Kang's disappearance

475
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:07,460
have to do with this coffin transport route?

476
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:11,400
Blind Zhang.

477
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:14,160
After you bumped into the coffin carriage that night,

478
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:15,560
did you touch the corpse?

479
00:26:16,120 --> 00:26:17,240
No, I didn't.

480
00:26:17,680 --> 00:26:19,680
Did the other party complain to you?

481
00:26:20,080 --> 00:26:21,120
No.

482
00:26:21,440 --> 00:26:23,880
He didn't say a word.

483
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:26,880
He must have been very angry.

484
00:26:31,520 --> 00:26:33,780
You didn't bump into me just now, did you?

485
00:26:36,840 --> 00:26:37,800
This proves

486
00:26:38,520 --> 00:26:40,440
the one lying in the coffin was a living person,

487
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:41,680
not a dead one.

488
00:26:43,800 --> 00:26:45,240
You mean

489
00:26:45,560 --> 00:26:47,760
the murderer was hiding in the coffin?

490
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:50,760
Any driver of a carriage

491
00:26:50,800 --> 00:26:52,660
would try to avoid a blind person.

492
00:26:52,960 --> 00:26:54,960
The suspect lay in the coffin,

493
00:26:55,040 --> 00:26:57,000
tying the deceased to the front of the carriage,

494
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:58,360
giving pedestrians at night

495
00:26:58,360 --> 00:27:01,020
the illusion that the deceased was still alive.

496
00:27:01,520 --> 00:27:03,280
Blind Zhang overturned the carriage,

497
00:27:03,280 --> 00:27:05,880
and happened to knock out the murderer inside.

498
00:27:05,920 --> 00:27:07,200
Sorry, sorry.

499
00:27:08,800 --> 00:27:10,060
Blind Zhang can't see,

500
00:27:10,560 --> 00:27:11,760
he naturally thought

501
00:27:12,120 --> 00:27:13,380
that inside the coffin

502
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:15,880
was a corpse.

503
00:27:20,280 --> 00:27:21,160
This horse

504
00:27:21,240 --> 00:27:22,920
is familiar with the transport route.

505
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:23,720
In my opinion,

506
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:25,640
the place it stops

507
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:27,760
from where the suspect hid the body

508
00:27:27,760 --> 00:27:28,920
won't be too far.

509
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:32,480
Good boy.

510
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:35,100
I'll rely on you to solve the case.

511
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:40,360
Good boy,

512
00:27:40,520 --> 00:27:42,000
finding this is all your credit.

513
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:43,460
Here's some grass for you.

514
00:27:44,320 --> 00:27:45,520
Why is he acting so weird,

515
00:27:45,520 --> 00:27:46,580
