516
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:48,240
What's his background?

517
00:27:48,360 --> 00:27:50,290
How come I haven't seen him before?

518
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:52,320
What kind of place is Yichun Brothel?

519
00:27:52,320 --> 00:27:53,440
A place of pleasure.

520
00:27:53,440 --> 00:27:55,480
The people there are either playboys or vagabonds.

521
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:57,040
How many good people can there be?

522
00:27:57,040 --> 00:27:59,680
For this unsolved case that has baffled the authorities for days,

523
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:02,360
he actually deduced without any clues from the remains,

524
00:28:02,360 --> 00:28:05,080
the suspect's modus operandi.

525
00:28:05,240 --> 00:28:06,480
He is really something.

526
00:28:06,480 --> 00:28:07,880
Why don't you believe it?

527
00:28:09,120 --> 00:28:10,240
Got it. Right here.

528
00:28:10,280 --> 00:28:11,520
Dug it out. Found it.

529
00:28:41,160 --> 00:28:42,640
How could this happen?

530
00:28:42,760 --> 00:28:45,200
How could this happen? How could this happen?

531
00:28:45,200 --> 00:28:46,680
How could this happen?

532
00:28:50,720 --> 00:28:52,320
Next month,

533
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:56,640
you were supposed to marry Miss Wanqing.

534
00:28:58,840 --> 00:29:00,040
Who is Wanqing?

535
00:29:03,400 --> 00:29:04,960
Nanrong Wanqing,

536
00:29:05,800 --> 00:29:08,200
the eldest daughter of Anning Music House.

537
00:29:08,320 --> 00:29:09,120
Constable Su.

538
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:10,240
Coroner Li.

539
00:29:12,480 --> 00:29:14,800
Chief Su told you to go to Anning Music House immediately.

540
00:29:14,800 --> 00:29:15,930
Someone died there.

541
00:29:16,840 --> 00:29:18,770
How could it be such a coincidence?

542
00:29:19,480 --> 00:29:21,320
Our music house has been open for over a decade,

543
00:29:21,320 --> 00:29:23,720
and such a thing has never happened before.

544
00:29:25,480 --> 00:29:26,080
Oh my.

545
00:29:26,120 --> 00:29:26,960
Coroner Li,

546
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:28,600
you're finally here.

547
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:32,880
Did you catch the thieves?

548
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:34,360
Look at the masks of these two thieves.

549
00:29:34,360 --> 00:29:36,420
You can tell they are Mo Ya and Mo Ying.

550
00:29:36,720 --> 00:29:37,920
Let's put that aside.

551
00:29:38,600 --> 00:29:40,440
A body was found in the suburbs.

552
00:29:40,680 --> 00:29:41,800
Before the investigation started,

553
00:29:41,800 --> 00:29:44,400
