554
00:29:44,520 --> 00:29:46,080
How is the situation here?

555
00:29:46,240 --> 00:29:49,080
I just sent the girl's body back to the government office.

556
00:29:49,080 --> 00:29:50,480
I hadn't even warmed my seat

557
00:29:50,480 --> 00:29:51,480
