560
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:57,240
Where did she die?

561
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:08,040
Hurry!

562
00:30:09,520 --> 00:30:10,320
Come on.

563
00:30:11,080 --> 00:30:12,720
The dance tonight is going to be so beautiful.

564
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:13,240
Yes.

565
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:16,240
Good.

566
00:30:20,520 --> 00:30:21,600
It's so beautiful.

567
00:30:21,960 --> 00:30:23,040
It's wonderful.

568
00:30:23,800 --> 00:30:24,800
I told you so.

569
00:30:30,360 --> 00:30:31,640
Really good.

570
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:33,560
Well danced.

571
00:30:36,360 --> 00:30:39,080
Bravo!

572
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:42,520
So pretty.

573
00:30:42,560 --> 00:30:44,160
Encore!

574
00:30:48,960 --> 00:30:49,800
Wanrou!

575
00:30:50,360 --> 00:30:51,440
Wanrou is back!

576
00:30:51,560 --> 00:30:53,560
Wanrou is back. She wants to kill me.

577
00:30:53,640 --> 00:30:54,300
She's back.

578
00:30:54,320 --> 00:30:54,880
What?

579
00:30:56,480 --> 00:30:57,640
Wanrou is back.

580
00:30:58,880 --> 00:31:00,010
She wants to kill me.

581
00:31:23,880 --> 00:31:27,080
The deceased suffered extensive burns all over the body.

582
00:31:27,320 --> 00:31:29,560
The skin and flesh are blackened and carbonized,

583
00:31:29,560 --> 00:31:31,280
facial features are indistinguishable,

584
00:31:31,280 --> 00:31:32,740
and nails have fallen off.

585
00:31:35,040 --> 00:31:36,400
But facing one side.

586
00:31:38,480 --> 00:31:42,410
The chest and abdomen are burst open, and deformed organs are visible.

587
00:31:42,600 --> 00:31:44,320
In the oral cavity, nasal cavity, and throat,

588
00:31:44,320 --> 00:31:46,040
there is a large amount of soot.

589
00:31:46,040 --> 00:31:47,720
The cause of death was burning by fire

590
00:31:47,720 --> 00:31:50,450
and inhalation of dense smoke while struggling.

591
00:31:52,320 --> 00:31:53,160
Coroner Li.

592
00:31:53,800 --> 00:31:55,720
Judging from the scene,

593
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:57,400
it should be that while she was dancing,

594
00:31:57,400 --> 00:31:59,200
the many flames lit around her

595
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:00,920
ignited her skirt,

596
00:32:00,960 --> 00:32:02,760
causing this disaster.

597
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:05,720
Is that really how she died?

598
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:08,440
This is completely impossible.

599
00:32:09,840 --> 00:32:11,280
If clothing catches fire

600
00:32:11,320 --> 00:32:13,480
and the flames grow to burn a person to death,

601
00:32:13,480 --> 00:32:15,160
it takes time.

602
00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:17,210
But everyone clearly said just now

603
00:32:17,280 --> 00:32:19,080
that she was burned to death instantly.

604
00:32:19,080 --> 00:32:20,810
Such a sudden and absolute end,

605
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:22,320
there must be something suspicious behind it.

606
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:24,880
Do you have the right to speak like this when the government is handling a case?

607
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:25,520
Alright.

608
00:32:29,760 --> 00:32:30,880
Who are you?

609
00:32:34,440 --> 00:32:35,400
I am Jueming.

610
00:32:35,680 --> 00:32:37,480
I was just with Miss Wang Mingzhu

611
00:32:37,520 --> 00:32:39,560
finding the bones of her brother, Wang Kang.

612
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:40,880
I came to Anning Brothel specifically

613
00:32:40,880 --> 00:32:42,280
to inform his betrothed.

614
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:50,920
Mingzhu.

615
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:54,480
Is what he said true?

616
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:56,720
Is my fiancé, Wang Kang,

617
00:32:57,800 --> 00:32:59,360
really dead?

618
00:33:09,520 --> 00:33:11,560
Who killed him?

619
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:21,890
My daughter.

620
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:23,840
Alright.

621
00:33:26,960 --> 00:33:27,720
Alright.

622
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:31,200
Two murders occurred consecutively tonight,

623
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:33,200
causing great grief

624
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:35,340
to the relatives of two families.

625
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:38,200
As a government constable,

626
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:40,200
I express my sympathy.

627
00:33:40,520 --> 00:33:41,720
I also promise you

628
00:33:42,040 --> 00:33:44,480
that the government will thoroughly investigate this case

629
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:45,920
and give you an explanation.

630
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:46,980
Alright, alright.

631
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:49,680
Alright, Su Lang.

632
00:33:49,760 --> 00:33:50,440
Yes.

633
00:33:50,560 --> 00:33:52,760
These two are not involved in this case.

634
00:33:52,760 --> 00:33:54,420
Please escort them out first.

635
00:33:55,000 --> 00:33:55,800
Let's go.

636
00:33:55,920 --> 00:33:56,640
Wait.

637
00:33:59,760 --> 00:34:01,120
You just said

638
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:02,680
there must be something fishy about this matter.

639
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:04,080
Why don't you elaborate?

640
00:34:04,120 --> 00:34:06,040
I'd like to hear your assessment.

